{"tid":2248112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[The Watcher]連哨台都食人血饅頭 仲唔黎圍屌","createTime":"2020-10-18T11:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T12:09:12.000Z","uid":377761,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22d807670b069ee3a6a10a80dbf562898a39831a","tid":2248112,"uid":377761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T11:00:09.000Z","msg":"The Watcher 狩望者哨兵頻道係其中一個香港抗爭者嘅支援頻道，主要工作包括報告香港警察位置及行動、撰寫哨兵相關抗爭教學，及其他抗爭支援服務。<br />\n<br />\n我地Admin團隊已經離開香港，相信稍為有d消息來源嘅手足都知點解，就唔解釋太多。雖然身處海外，The Watcher哨兵頻道服務將不受影響繼續運作，支援香港手足繼續對抗極權。<br />\n<br />\n同時，我地希望進一步為香港抗爭者作出支援，部份計劃需要一定資源配合，現打算以眾籌方法籌務資金。我地會以最後籌得資金水平決定推出幾多服務，就算最後籌唔到任何錢，我地仍會盡力為手足服務，但只專注處理<p class=\"left\"></p>資訊為主的服務。<br />\n<br />\n期望推出嘅服務包括：<br />\n<br />\n籌唔到錢都做：<br />\n<br />\n-以文宣宣傳讓英國企業了解香港情況及推廣僱用香港人，同時手足亦可免費自行印製我地嘅文宣，在BNO visa審批前先行接觸希望從事行業嘅僱主<br />\n<br />\n-租屋配對：根據唔同嘅因素，協助有意前往英國嘅手足係租屋上配對，多人分擔租金減低開支<br />\n<br />\n-搵工翻譯：不少勞動同技術工種對英文要求唔高，但搵工果陣仍需一定溝通能力/文字理解能力，首階段可先行提供有限度地區翻譯服務同全英國文字翻譯服務。<br />\n<br />\n&pound;1000以上：<br />\n<br />\n- 設立網站列出會考慮僱用香港人嘅職位及企業資料<br />\n<br />\n&pound;5000以上：<br />\n<br />\n- 文宣印刷費用支援：如英國各地手足有意協助本計劃宣傳，可以印製文宣張貼，我地會比作出費用支援，只需事後提供單據及實物相片即可<br />\n<br />\n- 贈送小禮物答謝支持本計劃嘅英國僱主，鼓勵發展當地黃店網絡<br />\n<br />\n&pound;100,000 - &pound;150,000 或以上：<br />\n- 高風險手足免息貸款計劃 <br />\na. 以英國政府要求之生活資金作貸款金額<br />\nb. 驗證身份手續將會於抵達英國後開始<br />\nc. 預計還款期將於連續受僱滿2個月開始，以每月工資10%-40%償還，具體比例視人工釐定<br />\n<br />\n更具體方案請參閱眾籌page<br />\n如有任何意見/查詢/討論，請到The Watcher UK 公海 @watcheruk 留言，或者pm @TheWatcherUK，請唔好用報哨bot/意見bot，以免干擾哨頻運作。<br />\n<br />\n為避免fb Share post/share眾籌page 可能觸犯香港嘅on9法例，我地會係fb同眾籌page將部份用字更改/分開post出，請大家如果支持我地，麻煩自行揀合適嘅post黎share🙇🏻&zwj;♀🙇🏻&zwj;♀🙇🏻&zwj;♀🙇🏻&zwj;♂🙇🏻&zwj;♂🙇🏻<br />\n<br />\n眾籌Page：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/the-watcher-uk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fthe-watcher-uk%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1axTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=f8654408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/the-watcher-uk/</a> <br />\n<br />\nThe Watcher UK Channel <a href=\"https://t.me/s/the_watcher_UK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fs%2Fthe_watcher_UK&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1axTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=b5cedac3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/s/the_watcher_UK</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Watcher UK 公海 <a href=\"https://t.me/s/watcheruk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fs%2Fwatcheruk&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1axTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=efdd8c3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/s/watcheruk</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Watcher UK 手足登記表<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/Yoq6rJwRCsbtqT8m7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FYoq6rJwRCsbtqT8m7&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1axTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=eb9ad570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/Yoq6rJwRCsbtqT8m7</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Watcher UK Employer Registration form<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/3duwvPNjtNPNxnXp9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F3duwvPNjtNPNxnXp9&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1axTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=70c88260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/3duwvPNjtNPNxnXp9</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Watcher UK facebook page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/The-Watcher-UK-115171697028656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FThe-Watcher-UK-115171697028656&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1axTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=c8a56e8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/The-Watcher-UK-115171697028656</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Watcher 狩望者哨兵頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/s/The_watcher_channel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fs%2FThe_watcher_channel&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1axTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=6c0f184a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/s/The_watcher_channel</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Watcher 狩望者哨兵教學資訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/s/Sentinel_Training\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihk